      <title>hexo学习笔记</title>
      <link href="/2023/04/15/Hexo%E5%AD%A6%E4%B9%A0%E7%AC%94%E8%AE%B0/"/>
      <url>/2023/04/15/Hexo%E5%AD%A6%E4%B9%A0%E7%AC%94%E8%AE%B0/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>简介：学习ing</p><p>参考：<a href="https://blog.csdn.net/qq_38157825/article/details/112782997">https://blog.csdn.net/qq_38157825/article/details/112782997</a></p><h2 id="hexo常用命令"><a href="#hexo常用命令" class="headerlink" title="hexo常用命令"></a>hexo常用命令</h2><figure class="highlight verilog"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br><span class="line">31</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">hexo init      初始化一个本地文件夹为网站的根目录</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">hexo clean     命令用于清理缓存文件</span><br><span class="line">hexo c         简写</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">hexo <span class="keyword">generate</span>  生成静态文件</span><br><span class="line">hexo g         简写</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">hexo server    启动本地服务器 可以先在线预览</span><br><span class="line">hexo s</span><br><span class="line">           可以加一些参数</span><br><span class="line">           -p    选项，指定服务器端口，默认为 <span class="number">4000</span></span><br><span class="line">           -i    选项，指定服务器 IP 地址，默认为 <span class="number">0</span><span class="variable">.0</span><span class="variable">.0</span><span class="variable">.0</span></span><br><span class="line">           -s    选项，静态模式 ，仅提供 public 文件夹中的文件并禁用文件监视</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">hexo deploy    部署到github网站</span><br><span class="line">hexo d</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">hexo <span class="keyword">new</span> post <span class="string">&quot;我的第一篇博客&quot;</span>  新建文章命令</span><br><span class="line">目录../source/_posts/          生成文件位置</span><br><span class="line">如：我的第一篇博客<span class="variable">.md</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">在线预览 默认：<span class="number">127</span><span class="variable">.0</span><span class="variable">.0</span><span class="variable">.1</span>：<span class="number">4000</span>  进阶版本命令</span><br><span class="line">hexo c &amp;&amp; hexo g &amp;&amp; hexo s</span><br><span class="line">上传github服务器</span><br><span class="line">hexo g &amp;&amp; hexo d</span><br><span class="line"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="编辑md文件"><a href="#编辑md文件" class="headerlink" title="编辑md文件"></a>编辑md文件</h2><figure class="highlight subunit"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">categories: 文章类别</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">tags:</span></span><br><span class="line">- 学习ing</span><br><span class="line">- hexo样式学习</span><br><span class="line">- 教程</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="首页图片"><a href="#首页图片" class="headerlink" title="首页图片"></a>首页图片</h2><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&lt;img src=&quot;http://cdn-hw-static.shanhutech.cn/bizhi/staticwp/202212/6a67c8b1f6cdae8bc92fbd85e9f15967--1346859535.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;width:100%&quot; /&gt;  </span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="标题"><a href="#标题" class="headerlink" title="标题"></a>标题</h2><figure class="highlight clean"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">## 标题<span class="number">1</span></span><br><span class="line">### 标题<span class="number">2</span></span><br><span class="line">#### 标题<span class="number">3</span></span><br><span class="line">##### 标题<span class="number">4</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="代码设置"><a href="#代码设置" class="headerlink" title="代码设置"></a>代码设置</h2><figure class="highlight autohotkey"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">需要上下输入 ``` 包裹住代码</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="URL跳转"><a href="#URL跳转" class="headerlink" title="URL跳转"></a>URL跳转</h2><figure class="highlight less"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="selector-tag">Welcome</span> <span class="selector-tag">to</span> <span class="selector-attr">[Hexo]</span>(<span class="attribute">https</span>:<span class="comment">//hexo.io/)!</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><hr />]]></content>
      
      
